Faithfully play back a recorded session in an interactive TUI (SRS FR-3)

Usage: hh replay [OPTIONS] [SESSION]

Arguments:
  [SESSION]  Session short id, full id, or `last` (most recent). Defaults to `last`

Options:
      --web   Export a self-contained HTML replay page to a temp file and print its path, instead of opening the interactive TUI. Does not need a terminal, does not open a browser, and does not start a server
  -h, --help  Print help

Example:
  hh replay last
  hh replay a1b2c3
  hh replay last --web
